{"id":232327695,"title":"#請益 Socket.io運用https的方法","content":"我在做一個即時互動的網頁，因此用了node.js裡的socket.io\n把網頁開在port 3000，因為80跟443已經放了別的網頁\nhttp://i.imgur.com/nU2rzlt.png\n\n我必須要使用https協定因為我需要在其他https網頁運用這個應用\n如果沒有把socket.io運用https協定會出現mixed content問題\n\n\n現在如果我用上面的code，https://DomainName:3000是可用的\n只是瀏覽器會說這個網頁實際是不安全的\n如果一切運作在http是正常沒問題，可是https就遇到很多障礙\nhttp://i.imgur.com/aqZCNmH.png\n\n我的伺服器是用apache，有看到網路上說可以運用reverse proxy來實現\n可是我看了很多資料，還是無法解決\n希望有人可以幫助我一下\n這個問題卡了我整個專題一個禮拜都沒新進度了","excerpt":"我在做一個即時互動的網頁，因此用了node.js裡的socket.io，把網頁開在port 3000，因為80跟443已經放了別的網頁，我必須要使用https協定因為我需要在其他https網頁運用這個","anonymousSchool":false,"anonymousDepartment":true,"pinned":false,"forumId":"a6dc1b6b-0aca-4004-86c8-3af6cdbfad23","replyId":null,"createdAt":"2019-10-18T19:42:54.803Z","updatedAt":"2019-10-18T19:42:54.803Z","commentCount":9,"likeCount":6,"tags":[],"topics":["SocketIO","https","web","程式"],"supportedReactions":null,"withNickname":false,"reportReason":"","hiddenByAuthor":false,"meta":{"layout":"classic"},"forumName":"軟體工程師","forumAlias":"softwareengineer","school":"逢甲大學","replyTitle":null,"gender":"M","personaSubscriptable":null,"reactions":[{"id":"286f599c-f86a-4932-82f0-f5a06f1eca03","count":6}],"hidden":false,"customStyle":null,"isSuspiciousAccount":false,"layout":"classic","withImages":true,"withVideos":false,"media":[{"url":"http://i.imgur.com/nU2rzlt.png"},{"url":"http://i.imgur.com/aqZCNmH.png"}],"reportReasonText":"","mediaMeta":[{"id":"89c89c9e-05ea-48b4-b074-7d45857afb97","url":"https://i.imgur.com/nU2rzltl.jpg","normalizedUrl":"https://i.imgur.com/nU2rzltl.jpg","thumbnail":"https://i.imgur.com/nU2rzltl.jpg","type":"image/thumbnail","tags":["ANNOTATED"],"createdAt":"2019-10-18T19:42:54.803Z","updatedAt":"2019-10-18T19:42:54.803Z"},{"id":"89c89c9e-05ea-48b4-b074-7d45857afb97","url":"http://i.imgur.com/nU2rzlt.png","normalizedUrl":"https://imgur.com/nU2rzlt","thumbnail":"https://i.imgur.com/nU2rzltl.jpg","type":"image/imgur","tags":["ANNOTATED"],"createdAt":"2019-10-18T19:42:54.803Z